 <section_number>8-2186</section_number>
 <catch_line>PROHIBITED USES OF REUSE WATER.</catch_line>
 <order_by>8-2186</order_by>
 <text>
  <section prefix="(1)">	Human consumption.
</section>
  <section prefix="(2)">	Irrigation of direct food chain crops.
</section>
  <section prefix="(3)">	Swimming pools, hot tubs, spas, or similar uses.
</section>
  <section prefix="(4)">	Direct reuse as raw potable water supply.
</section>
  <section prefix="(5)">	Any uses that are specifically prohibited under the North Carolina Administrative Code regulating the use of reclaimed or reuse water. 
(Ord. No. 2006-100, ยง1, 9-19-06) 
</section>
